[div class=p 
	[em 
		"The Death and Return of Superman
	]em
	" is a licensed beat 'em up that was developed by Blizzard and published by Sunsoft. It is an adaptation of the DC Comics story arc 
	[em 
		"The Death of Superman
	]em
	", where Doomsday comes to Earth and kills Superman and four superpowered beings then coming out and claiming to be Superman resurrected. These beings are now known as Cyborg Superman, the Eradicator, the Conner Kent version of Superboy, and Steel. Are any of them actually Superman? And what do all the punk-looking enemies have to do with all of that?  You'll have to play the game and witness all the obligatory defeats to find out.
